If my AI-Operated Space Zoo company, which currently operates zero space zo=
os, promises to generate $100 million in free cash flow by 2028, investors =
will apply a very skeptical Belief Rate, somewhere in the 0.5% range. That,=
 plus the higher discount rate, will give my AI-Operated Space Zoo company =
so low a valuation that it will be hard for me to find investors willing to=
