Caveating once again that these numbers are all made up, that I=E2=80=99m n=
ot running a full DCF model, and that I=E2=80=99m using a Belief Rate on ol=
d numbers as a catch-all for belief, adjusted projections, and a very real =
hit to the number of customers willing to pay $450k to fly to space in this=
