ning. Future luxury space travel is a near-perfect vessel for belief =E2=80=
=93 there=E2=80=99s not much else to go on at this point =E2=80=93 and when=
 people=E2=80=99s belief falters in a bad market, it=E2=80=99s retrospectiv=
ely very obvious that future luxury space travel was going to be hit a lot =
harder than the broader market.=C2=A0
I say =E2=80=9Cnear-perfect,=E2=80=9D because there is a perfect vessel for=
