While there=E2=80=99s a growing body of work on how to value various types =
of tokens, crypto=E2=80=99s valuation methodologies aren=E2=80=99t as stand=
ardized and broadly accepted as equities=E2=80=99. If you asked ten people =
how to value bitcoin, for example, you=E2=80=99d get answers ranging from s=
