pto prices jumped so high during the=
 2020-2021 bull run and why they=E2=80=99ve tanked so hard in this bear mar=
ket.=C2=A0
But the micro Belief Rate =E2=80=93 the Belief Rate tied to a particular ca=
tegory or asset =E2=80=93 can decouple from the macro Belief Rate given goo=
