ht, you&#8217;re getting a pretty steep Belief Discount right now.&#160;</p=
><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 =
0 20px 0;"><span>A related example is </span><strong>Snap</strong><span>, a=
